Btw here's a small demo of how to re-program the starting line of a
E/VGA card. Once re-programmed you see the second text page of the E/VGA
card.


{---------------------------------------------------------}
{  Project : Split screen for EGA & VGA                   }
{  Auteur  : Wim van der Vegt                             }
